webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Postcards showing Sweden’s first hunter Fashion to anchor in an ice-covered sea. The ship was photographed from an elevated position oblique to the rear from the starboard side. Adjacent to the ship is a ship boat moored. In the background, a banded larger warship, probably armored ships and cannon boats, is visible in front of a archipelago - https://www.europeana.eu/item/916108/smm_mm_photo_D14989_11. Marinmuseum - https://digitaltmuseum.se/021017992603. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
